        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "4. Business Logic and Workflow"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "orderedList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Set NOCOUNT ON",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": This prevents the sending of DONE_IN_PROC messages to the client for each statement in a stored procedure, which can improve performance by reducing network traffic."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Retrieve Latest Billing Period",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The procedure selects the most recent billing period from the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Batch.FileStep",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " table, which is also present in the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "NYPA.UploadNYPAAccountBillingPreload",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " table."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Execute Preprocessing Procedure",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": It calls the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Nypa.usp_PreProcessingMatchCoverLetterToEfileCoversheet",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " stored procedure, passing several parameters including the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@shorePowerCredit",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ". The procedure is expected to perform some preprocessing tasks related to matching cover letters to e-file coversheets."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Update Success Status",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": If the preprocessing procedure executes without errors, the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Batch.FileStep",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " table is updated to mark the step as successful ("
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "IsSuccess = 1",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ") for the retrieved billing period."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Error Handling",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": If an error occurs during the execution of the preprocessing procedure, the catch block captures detailed error information and updates the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Batch.FileStep",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " table to indicate failure ("
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "IsSuccess = 0",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "), along with an error message and details."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
